TiledArray::expressions::VariableList Class Reference

Documentation

Variable list manages a list variable strings.

Each variable is separated by commas. All spaces are ignored and removed from variable list. So, "a c" will be converted to "ac" and will be considered a single variable. All variables must be unique.
